# JAQL Documentation

## ADR Format

Architecture Decision Records live in `docs/adr/`.

- Filename: `ADR-<NNNN>-<kebab-case-title>.md` (4-digit zero-padded number)
- Template reference: [docs/adr/ADR-0001-conan2-package-manager.md](docs/adr/ADR-0001-conan2-package-manager.md)
- New ADRs start with `Status: Proposed`

Determine the next ADR number by listing existing files in `docs/adr/`.

## Writing Style

- Link to authoritative docs rather than duplicating standards.
- Coding standards belong in `docs/coding-standards.md`, not scattered across ADRs.
- Use the `@jaql-new-adr` skill to scaffold new ADRs.
